title: How I Started Dressing Vintage | Jasmine Chiswell
description: In today's episode, we will talk about real-life Hollywood glam coming from Jasmine Chiswell. She is known on social media with millions and millions of followers for her vintage style. Recently, she purchased the honeymoon House of Joe DiMaggio and Marilyn Monroe, which is pretty neat, considering she may have also adopted a few ghosts from that. Jasmine will talk about how she came about her vintage style and how you can accomplish this, as well. She will also share a few stories about the ghosts that have popped up in her household.
